Invocation Name: lunch spinner
des: Sometimes it is hard to decide what to eat and where to eat. Why not have a lunch-spinner to give it a quick spin and decide for you? Just say, Alexa, ask Lunch Spinner, you will be delighted that decision can be so effortlessly made and in the end, you get a fortune cookie quote delivered to you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
